pageType: content
background:
  type: solid
  color: "$offwhite"
elements:
  # Section number
  - elementId: sec-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 30, 120, 24]
    content:
      fontSize: 12
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      color: "#0F3D354D"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>09 / 10</p>

  # Section eyebrow
  - elementId: eyebrow
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 58, 200, 24]
    content:
      style: "$eyebrow"
      color: "$primary"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>PRIORITY ACTIONS</p>

  # Section heading
  - elementId: heading
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 86, 600, 120]
    content:
      style: "$sectionHeading"
      text: |
        <p>If I Were<br><em style="color:#0F3D35;">The Founder</em></p>

  # Three action cards
  # Card 1
  - elementId: a1-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [80, 216, 370, 300]
    shapeName: roundRect
    adjustments: [4000]
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "#FFFFFF"
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "$border"

  - elementId: a1-header
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [80, 216, 370, 60]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"

  - elementId: a1-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [100, 216, 60, 60]
    content:
      fontSize: 32
      fontFamily: "SortsMillGoudy"
      color: "#FFFFFF20"
      align: [center, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>01</p>

  - elementId: a1-label
    elementType: text
    bounds: [160, 216, 270, 60]
    content:
      fontSize: 12
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      color: "#FFFFFF60"
      letterSpacing: 1.5
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>BRAND STORY</p>

  - elementId: a1-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [100, 296, 330, 56]
    content:
      fontSize: 17
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      color: "$text"
      lineHeight: 1.3
      text: |
        <p><strong>Build the story before the next funding round</strong></p>

  - elementId: a1-body
    elementType: text
    bounds: [100, 358, 330, 90]
    content:
      fontSize: 14
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      color: "$textLight"
      lineHeight: 1.5
      text: |
        <p>A founder manifesto, a design journal, a factory film. Make the Indian supply chain the brand story — not a footnote. Show the craftspeople.</p>

  - elementId: a1-impact
    elementType: text
    bounds: [100, 452, 330, 40]
    content:
      fontSize: 12
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      color: "$primary"
      lineHeight: 1.4
      text: |
        <p><strong>Cost: near-zero · Impact: transforms brand identity</strong></p>

  # Card 2
  - elementId: a2-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [466, 216, 370, 300]
    shapeName: roundRect
    adjustments: [4000]
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "#FFFFFF"
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "$border"

  - elementId: a2-header
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [466, 216, 370, 60]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"

  - elementId: a2-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [486, 216, 60, 60]
    content:
      fontSize: 32
      fontFamily: "SortsMillGoudy"
      color: "#FFFFFF20"
      align: [center, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>02</p>

  - elementId: a2-label
    elementType: text
    bounds: [546, 216, 270, 60]
    content:
      fontSize: 12
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      color: "#FFFFFF60"
      letterSpacing: 1.5
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>COMMUNITY OVER CELEBRITY</p>

  - elementId: a2-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [486, 296, 330, 44]
    content:
      fontSize: 17
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      color: "$text"
      lineHeight: 1.3
      text: |
        <p><strong>Credibility ambassadors, not just reach</strong></p>

  - elementId: a2-body
    elementType: text
    bounds: [486, 348, 330, 100]
    content:
      fontSize: 14
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      color: "$textLight"
      lineHeight: 1.5
      text: |
        <p>50 high-credibility advocates in design, architecture, and startup culture. The Bellroy model: laser focus on a niche, then expand.</p>

  - elementId: a2-impact
    elementType: text
    bounds: [486, 458, 330, 40]
    content:
      fontSize: 12
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      color: "$primary"
      lineHeight: 1.4
      text: |
        <p><strong>Target: 50 advocates · CAC reduction: ~30%</strong></p>

  # Card 3
  - elementId: a3-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [852, 216, 370, 300]
    shapeName: roundRect
    adjustments: [4000]
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "#FFFFFF"
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "$border"

  - elementId: a3-header
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [852, 216, 370, 60]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"

  - elementId: a3-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [872, 216, 60, 60]
    content:
      fontSize: 32
      fontFamily: "SortsMillGoudy"
      color: "#FFFFFF20"
      align: [center, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>03</p>

  - elementId: a3-label
    elementType: text
    bounds: [932, 216, 270, 60]
    content:
      fontSize: 12
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      color: "#FFFFFF60"
      letterSpacing: 1.5
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>EVERY BAG A BILLBOARD</p>

  - elementId: a3-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [872, 296, 330, 56]
    content:
      fontSize: 17
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      color: "$text"
      lineHeight: 1.3
      text: |
        <p><strong>Emboss the three-wave mark on every product</strong></p>

  - elementId: a3-body
    elementType: text
    bounds: [872, 358, 330, 90]
    content:
      fontSize: 14
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      color: "$textLight"
      lineHeight: 1.5
      text: |
        <p>2L customers × 50 airport impressions per journey × 4 journeys per year = 40 Cr brand impressions annually at zero cost.</p>

  - elementId: a3-impact
    elementType: text
    bounds: [872, 452, 330, 40]
    content:
      fontSize: 12
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      color: "$primary"
      lineHeight: 1.4
      text: |
        <p><strong>40 Crore impressions · ₹0 incremental spend</strong></p>

  # Final statement
  - elementId: fs-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [80, 540, 1120, 100]
    shapeName: roundRect
    adjustments: [4000]
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"

  - elementId: fs-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [108, 546, 800, 88]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      fontFamily: "SortsMillGoudy"
      color: "$background"
      lineHeight: 1.4
      align: [left, middle]
      text: |
        <p>"The segment is not wrong. The segment is not even targeting the wrong people. What needs to change is the brand's ability to speak the emotional language that segment responds to."</p>
